lead_paragraph: Tottenham Hotspur were not about to take any risks with Dele Alli on Saturday but when the teenager was called on to deliver off the bench against Watford, the team were again rewarded by a match-winning gem of a show.

headline.print_headline: Alli Boxes Clever and Proves a Knockout for Soaring Spurs
